    "en": {
      "title": "Don't allow Ranil to be president for a single day",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "TNA MPs MA Sumanthran and Sanakyan Rajamanikkam have requested the protesters not to allow Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe to hold the office of President even for a single day.",
        "They have made this demand during the discussion held yesterday (13) with the empty face protestors.",
        "They also said that if Ranil Wickremesinghe had not run and accepted the post of Prime Minister, Gotabaya Rajapaksa would have resigned from the presidency two months ago."
      ],
